# Sample Project Engineering Rules

This is the sample project from the Engineering Constitution framework.

It follows the [Engineering Constitution](../../constitution/CONSTITUTION.md).

## Before Making Changes

Read:

- `constitution/CONSTITUTION.md` — universal engineering principles
- `README.md` — project purpose and setup
- `TODO.md` — roadmap and known issues
- `CHANGELOG.md` — recent changes

## Standards

- Follow existing code style and project conventions.
- Add or update tests for all behavior changes.
- Update documentation when behavior or setup changes.
- Update `TODO.md` with discovered work.
- Update `CHANGELOG.md` for user-facing changes.

## Project-Specific Rules

- This is a sample project. Treat it as an illustrative example only.
